_sText:
My first three GG(gungame) maps.
gg_magma_nemesis can also be used as a ka_ if wanted.
Was just wondering why i couldnt find any GG section etc. Did i miss it?
In gg_magma_nemesis you can plant the bomb in two locations (tower via teleport) and also the centre section. The lava can also rise if you press a button on a cliff edge. Useful for killing any campers.
Anyhow, enjoy the maps!
Feel free to post some feed-back. Im interested to what people think of my GG maps compared to others ive made.
EDIT:Logos have been removed. (beermonkeys)
